product.name: DREAM PAIRS Women's Closed Pointed Toe Low Chunky Heels Pumps Ankle Strap Wedding Business Dressy Shoes
product.bullet_points:
• Upper: faux leather upper; Outsole: TPR anti-slip outsole; Padded: latex insole.
• Low chunky heel pumps shoes, 2 inches heel height are the perfect height for all-day wear and won't tire your feet out.
• Ankle strap with buckle closure, matching a strap across the instep and continues to the heel, add an extra touch of elegance.
• Classic pointed toe pumps shoes, matching closed toe design and structural low block heel, better show your charm on any daily or wedding occasion.
• Clean silhouette lines is sleeker than ever, from jeans to skirts, suits, can easily match all types of clothes in your wardrobe.
